The Rector of Auchi Polytechnic, Edo State, Dr. Momodu Sanusi Jimah is dead. The Public Relations Officer of Auchi Polytechnic, Mr. Mustapha Oshiobugie, who confirmed the sad incident to newsmen on Saturday said he passed on Friday night at exactly 7.00 pm, NAN reports. “The institution is mourning following the demise of her rector who passed away on Friday at 7.00 pm after a brief illness”.
“I can confirm that he is no more and his remains will be committed to mother earth today Saturday at 10 am according to Muslim rites”, Oshiobugie said.